- So tied to them,

31:25.072 --> 31:27.039
- He's a criminal...
- That if you couldn't live with them,

31:27.074 --> 31:28.307
- and you're an addict!
- You couldn't live at all?

31:28.342 --> 31:29.942
[Sighs]

31:29.977 --> 31:32.478
I love how that feels.

31:32.512 --> 31:38.317
There's just us or there's
absolutely nothing.

31:38.352 --> 31:41.687
