way is when I'm with <i>him.</i>

31:45.092 --> 31:46.759
[Smacks lips, sighs]

31:49.263 --> 31:52.131
You can't save him anymore.

31:52.165 --> 31:54.834
They have the gun.

31:54.868 --> 31:57.770
